title: Ebro In The Morning - City Council Candidate Chi Ossé + Summer Jam Is Coming
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/8. The crew reminisces on yesterday's poop fiasco (39:00). 

Ebro thinks Vice President Kamala Harris played herself (13:30), Rosenberg preps to DJ in Jamaica, and Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (10:00, 33:00, & 55:00). Chi Ossé, the 23-year old Brooklyn City Council candidate talks with the crew (1:00:00).

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
